  <edu id="e1"><![CDATA[Paper books are a joy to read. Electronic books can never replace this feeling.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e2"><![CDATA[Many voracious readers love to hold books]]></edu>
  <edu id="e3"><![CDATA[and smell the ink and paper.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e4"><![CDATA[It could be argued that e-books are more convenient, and that is true.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e5"><![CDATA[However, the experience of reading a book is far more than just the information we get from it.]]></edu>
